Targetting all Desktop

These queries are based on devices "Screen Resolution". ["Screen Resolution" and "Browser Window Resolution" are diffrent]
Min-Width: Refers to everything greater than or equal to the amount given. 
Max-Width: Refers to everything less than or equal to the amount given.

/*--------------------------------------------------------------------- 10 - 12*/
@media only screen and (min-width : 1024px)  {body{background:AliceBlue;}}
/*-------------------------------------------------------------------------- 13*/
@media only screen and (min-width : 1280px)  {body{background:AntiqueWhite;}}
/*-------------------------------------------------------------------------- 15*/
@media only screen and (min-width : 1366px)  {body{background:purple;}}
/*-------------------------------------------------------------------------- 19*/
@media only screen and (min-width : 1440px)  {body{background:yellow;}}
/*-------------------------------------------------------------------------- 20*/
@media only screen and (min-width : 1600px)  {body{background:khaki;}}
/*-------------------------------------------------------------------------- 22*/
@media only screen and (min-width : 1680px)  {body{background:green;}}
/*--------------------------------------------------------------------- 23 - 24*/
@media only screen and (min-width : 1920px)  {body{background:blue;}}
